| 4 | [config.service.js](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/appwrite/config.service.js) | [getPosts([])](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/appwrite/config.service.js#88-100) called with unused arg | Harmless, but clean up the call in [AllPostPage](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/pages/AllPostPage.jsx#6-40) |
| 5 | [AuthLayout.jsx](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/components/AuthLayout.jsx) | Unused `{ set }` import from react-hook-form | Remove import |
| 6 | [Signup.jsx](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/components/Signup.jsx) | Unused `use` import | Remove |
| 7 | [PostForm.jsx](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/components/post-form/PostForm.jsx) | Unused `use` import | Remove |
| 8 | [PostForm.jsx](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/components/post-form/PostForm.jsx) | Missing `await` on [uploadFile](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/appwrite/config.service.js#101-115) (edit case) | Add `await` |
| 9 | [PostForm.jsx](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/components/post-form/PostForm.jsx) | `authorId` should be `userId` | Fix field name |
| 10 | [PostForm.jsx](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/components/post-form/PostForm.jsx) | `slugTransform` called with wrong args | Move `{ shouldValidate }` to `setValue` |
| 11 | [Header.jsx](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/components/header/Header.jsx) | Nav path `/posts` vs route `/all-posts` | Fix to `/all-posts` |
| 12 | [AllPostPage.jsx](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/pages/AllPostPage.jsx) | [PostCard](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/components/PostCard.jsx#5-21) receives wrong props | Use `{...post}` spread |
| 13 | [main.jsx](file:///run/media/manas/New%20Volume/PROGRAMAING/Web_Devlopment/React/Project/src/main.jsx) | Unused `BrowserRouter` import | Remove |

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
Since this project depends on a live Appwrite backend, automated tests aren't practical without mocking the entire backend. After applying fixes:

1. Run `npm run dev` and confirm the app starts without errors/warnings in the console
2. Verify the home page loads and shows posts (if any exist in the Appwrite DB)
3. Click "All Posts" in the header → should navigate to `/all-posts` (not `/posts`)
4. Verify post cards render correctly with images on both HomePage and AllPostPage
5. Create a new post → verify `userId` is stored correctly
6. Edit a post with a new image → verify the image updates (the `await` fix)
7. Signup and Login flows should work without console errors
